Let's look at all of these reasons: 1). as projectorion once said, what's the difference between a rocket and a missile, what's its pointing at.  The same airplanes that fly people across the ocean can deliver thousands of pounds of bombs both conventional and nuclear.  If you're opposed to proliferation, then you must oppose:<br>
