<br>
Wow, old Ted has his work cut out for him.<br>
<br>
2). there's a HUGE difference between a BB size pellet of deuterium and tritium being fused by lasers and a couple of pounds fused by a fission trigger.  It's like outlawing handguns and taking away a child's capgun.<br>
<br>
